                My name is BERTIN KABUNDI TSHISUAKA.
                I worked in more then seven companies as Maintenance Engineer in Georgia.

          While working in maintenace , I managed to get a bachelor degree in Information Technology software Engeneerinres.
          I am currently student in a Fullstack web developer bootcamp at Georgia Tech.
          I have learned to build a website from front end to backend with HTML,CSS,Javascript,using technologies and plateform like:
          bootstrap,Jquery,express ,sql,mangodb and GraphQl.
</p>
            <p className='content'>
